<version>1.0.0</version>
<doc>Robot Framework library for automating Windows desktop applications.

Supports WPF, WinForms, WinUI3, MAUI, Win32, Java Swing, Electron, Citrix/RDP.
Technology is auto-detected by default.

Import with the paths to your config and locators files:

| Library | DesktopAutomationLibrary | config_path=config.yaml | locator_path=locators.yaml |</doc>
<tags>
</tags>
